Simple but effective macro to save the current page
This demo works with the following page: Any
VERSION BUILD=8920312 RECORDER=FX 'Simple but effective macro to save the current page ' 'Ask for a name PROMPT &quot;Enter a Page Name&quot; !VAR1 NoName_Time_{{!NOW:yyyymmdd_hhnnss}} ' 'Save the page SAVEAS TYPE=CPL FOLDER=* FILE={{!VAR1}}

